title: Residences

children.text: A luxury experience at every turn.

From the moment you arrive at Walker’s Cay Luxury Resort & Marina on Marco Island, it’s evident that this is no ordinary coastal retreat. With a prime marina-front setting and breathtaking views of some of Florida’s most stunning west coast beaches, the gulf feels closer than ever. This exclusive curated collection of just 45 residences surprise and delight with expansive layouts, custom-designed interiors, and a selection of world-class amenities that redefine luxury living.

children.text: The Restaurant & Bar

Boasting stunning views and expertly crafted dishes, the main restaurant stands as San Marcos’ premier destination for refined dining at any hour. Its warm and elegant atmosphere creates the perfect backdrop for chic lunches, memorable dinners, and celebratory moments—no reservations necessary. The menu showcases the essence of coastal cuisine, featuring fresh, seasonal delights such as locally sourced seafood, farm-fresh produce, and more.
The Spa

Experience the essence of harmonious living. State-of-the-art cardio and strength training equipment, a dedicated free weights room, a versatile fitness space, and a serene yoga studio provide the perfect setting to sculpt your body. Find mental clarity in the tranquil relaxation of the on-site Spa and Wellness Center. Renew your spirit with indulgent offerings, including saunas, steam rooms, treatment rooms, and soothing jetted spas, thoughtfully designed to elevate your well-being.
The Marina

Enjoy unparalleled convenience with direct access to our marina just steps from your residence. Savor seamless yacht boarding and exclusive waterfront amenities, all designed to elevate your stay to extraordinary levels of comfort and sophistication.
The Pool
Basking in golden sunlight, lounge by the pool, cocktail in hand, as tranquil waves echo in the distance. Attentive service, plush cabanas, and a breathtaking sunset make it pure paradise.
Outdoor Dining

Indulge in a luxurious outdoor fine dining experience at a prestigious South Florida hotel, where gourmet cuisine meets breathtaking ocean views. As gentle sea breezes caress your skin, enjoy expertly crafted dishes paired with fine wines, all set against a backdrop of golden sands and rolling waves. Impeccable service and the soothing sounds of the surf create an unforgettable meal of elegance and indulgence by the beach.

Close to everywhere, worlds away.

Few places along Florida’s western coast rival the allure of Marco Island. Here, serene waters meet stunningly vivid sunsets, while upscale shopping, a dynamic cultural atmosphere, and modern entertainment in nearby Naples and direct (no bridges) boating access to Key West both offer endless indulgence. Add to that the pristine beaches, breathtaking natural beauty, and a warm, inviting community, and it’s clear why this gem is a truly unparalleled destination.
